data.title: Alfred Bester by Jad Smith (English) Hardcover Book 9780252040634
data.meta_description: Fans and scholars praise him as a genre-bending pioneer and cyberpunk forefather. Jad Smith traces the career of the unlikeliest of SF icons. In the 1960s, however, New Wave writers championed his work, and his reputation grew.
data.text: Will ship within 15 business days of receiving cleared payment. The seller has specified an extended handling time for this item.
